id]])\n|-\n!Best Midfielder\n|{{flagicon|COL}} [[James Rodr\u00edguez]] ([[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]])\n|-\n!Best Forward\n|{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Lionel Messi]] ([[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]])\n|-\n|}\n\n===Monthly===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Month\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[La Liga Manager of the Month|Manager of the Month]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[La Liga Player of the Month|Player of the Month]]\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Reference\n|-\n!Manager\n!Club\n!Player\n!Club\n|-\n|September\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[Nuno Esp\u00edrito Santo]]\n|Valencia\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Nolito]]\n|Celta Vigo\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/noticias/premios-bbva-a-los-mejores-de-septiembre Premios BBVA a los mejores de septiembre]; LFP.es 6 October 2014</ref>\n|-\n|October\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Carlo Ancelotti]]\n|Real Madrid\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Karim Benzema]]\n|Real Madrid\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-awards-for-the-best-of-october BBVA Awards for the best of October]; LFP.es 12 November 2014</ref>\n|-\n|November\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ernesto Valverde]]\n|Athletic Bilbao\n|{{flagicon|MEX}} [[Carlos Vela]]\n|Real Sociedad\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-awards-for-the-best-of-the-november BBVA Awards for the best of November]; LFP.es 10 December 2014</ref>\n|-\n|December\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[Nuno Esp\u00edrito Santo]]\n|Valencia\n|{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Luciano Vietto]]\n|Villarreal\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/the-bbva-prizes-for-decembers-best The BBVA Prizes for December's best]; LFP.es 14 January 2015</ref>\n|-\n|January\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Unai Emery]]\n|Sevilla\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Antoine Griezmann]]\n|Atl\u00e9tico Madrid\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/antoine-griezmann-liga-bbva-player-of-the-month-for-january Antoine Griezmann, Liga BBVA player of the month for January]; LFP.es, 5 February 2015</ref>\n|-\n|February\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[Nuno Esp\u00edrito Santo]]\n|Valencia\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Alberto Bueno]