cia]]\n| 30 May 2014\n|- \n| [[Espanyol]] \n| {{flagicon|Mexico}} [[Javier Aguirre]]\n| End of contract  \n| 16 May 2014\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Sergio (footballer, born 1976)|Sergio Gonz\u00e1lez Soriano]]\n| 28 May 2014\n|- \n| [[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Gerardo Martino]]\n| Resigned\n| 17 May 2014\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Luis Enrique (footballer)|Luis Enrique]]\n| 19 May 2014\n|- \n| [[Granada CF|Granada]] \n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Lucas Alcaraz]]\n| End of contract\n| 28 May 2014\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Joaqu\u00edn Caparr\u00f3s]]\n| 28 May 2014\n|- \n| [[Levante UD|Levante]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Joaqu\u00edn Caparr\u00f3s]]\n| Signed by Granada\n| 28 May 2014\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Mendilibar]]\n| 30 May 2014\n|- \n| [[Valencia CF|Valencia]]\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Juan Antonio Pizzi]]\n| Sacked\n| 2 July 2014\n| {{flagicon|Portugal}} [[Nuno Esp\u00edrito Santo]]\n| 4 July 2014\n|-\n| [[Deportivo de La Coru\u00f1a|Deportivo La Coru\u00f1a]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Fernando V\u00e1zquez]]\n| Sacked\n| 8 July 2014\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[V\u00edctor Fern\u00e1ndez]]\n| 10 July 2014\n|-\n| [[C\u00f3rdoba CF|C\u00f3rdoba]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Albert Ferrer]]\n| Sacked\n| 20 October 2014\n| 20th\n| {{flagicon|SRB}} [[Miroslav \u0110uki\u0107]]\n| 20 October 2014<ref>[http://www.marca.com/2014/10/20/futbol/equipos/cordoba/1413828417.html Djukic ser\u00e1 el entrenador del C\u00f3rdoba]; Marca.com, 20 October 2014</ref>\n|- \n| [[Levante UD|Levante]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Mendilibar]]\n| Sacked\n| 20 October 2014\n| 19th\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Lucas Alcaraz]]\n| 21 October 2014<ref>[http://futbol.as.com/futbol/2014/10/21/primera/1413910838_676627.html Lucas Alcaraz ya es el nuevo entrenador del Levante]; As.com, 21 October 2014</ref>\n|- \n| [[Real Sociedad]]\n| {{flagicon|Spain}} [[Jagoba Arrasate]]\n| Sacked\n| 2 November 2014\n| 19th\n| {{flagicon|Scotland}} [[David Moyes]]\n| 10 November 2014<r