olo]]\n|Sevilla\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-prizes-vitolo-best-liga-bbva-player-in-march BBVA Prizes: Vitolo, best Liga BBVA player in March]; LFP.es, 1 April 2015</ref><ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-prizes-ernesto-valverde-best-coach-in-the-liga-bbva-in-march BBVA Prizes: Ernesto Valverde, best coach in the Liga BBVA in March]; LFP.es, 2 April 2015</ref>\n|-\n|April\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Carlo Ancelotti]]\n|Real Madrid\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Antoine Griezmann]]\n|Atl\u00e9tico Madrid\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/carlo-ancelotti-named-liga-bbva-coach-of-the-month-for-april Carlo Ancelotti named Liga BBVA coach of the month for April]; LFP.es, 7 May 2015</ref><ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/antoine-griezmann-named-aprils-liga-bbva-player-of-the-month Antoine Griezmann named April's Liga BBVA player of the month]; LFP.es, 6 May 2015</ref>\n|-\n|May\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Jos\u00e9 Ram\u00f3n Sandoval]]\n|Granada\n|{{flagicon|POR}} [[Cristiano Ronaldo]]\n|Real Madrid\n|align=center|<ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-awards-jose-ramon-sandoval-liga-bbva-coach-of-the-month-for-may BBVA Awards: Jos\u00e9 Ram\u00f3n Sandoval, Liga BBVA coach of the month for May]; LFP.es, 4 June 2015</ref><ref>[http://www.lfp.es/en/news/bbva-awards-cristiano-ronaldo-chosen-as-liga-bbva-player-of-the-month-for-may BBVA Awards: Cristiano Ronaldo chosen as Liga BBVA player of the month for May]; LFP.es, 3 June 2015</ref>\n|}\n\n== Number of teams by autonomous community ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!\n![[Autonomous communities of Spain|Autonomous Community]]\n!Number of teams\n!Teams\n|-\n|rowspan=1|1\n|{{flagu|Andalusia}}||align=center|5||[[UD Almer\u00eda|Almer\u00eda]], [[C\u00f3rdoba CF|C\u00f3rdoba]], [[Granada CF|Granada]], [[M\u00e1laga CF|M\u00e1laga]] and [[Sevilla FC|Sevilla]]\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2\n|{{flagu|Madrid|name=Community of Madrid}}||rowspan=\"2\" align=center|4||[[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]], [[Getafe CF|Getafe]], [[Rayo Vallecano]] a